reviewText:
NOTHING on the big front of the box or any of the characters or movies are in the collection.  This is the same old tired CR*P that Mill Creek and their ilk have been cranking out for years.  They REALLY (I am serious) should be sued for false representation.

I must have been on drugs when I made this buy.  I should have know better.

I hope the plastic burns well.  I thought I'd use it for a fireplace starter this winter!
